These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, 7up
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: horror, musical
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: parkour, tennis
The people use 2 different means of transport: subway, airplane
1. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the person who's sport is tennis##3
2. the person drinking 7up is in an even position##4
3. the person watching musical movies is the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | iced-tea  | 7up   |
| Movie-Genre   | musical     | horror   |
| Sport         | tennis | parkour |
| Transport     | subway | airplane    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
There 2 different types of food: mango, onion
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: scientific, animation
2 different pets are kept: hedgehog, ferret
The people use 2 different means of transport: snowmobile, scooter
1. the owner of the ferret is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching scientific movies is the person driving the scooter##1
3. the person eating onion is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Food          | mango     | onion |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | scientific  |
| Pet           | ferret         | hedgehog     |
| Transport     | snowmobile   | scooter    |

 #################################

 
