.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  entrepreneur, dancer
There are 2 different nationalities: brazilian, polish
2 different pets are kept: snake, pony
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rowing, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is in an even position##4
2. the polish is on the far left or far right##3
3. the dancer is the brazilian##1
4. the owner of the snake is on the left of the polish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Job           | dancer | entrepreneur    |
| Nationality   | brazilian       | polish |
| Pet           | snake         | pony    |
| Sport         | rowing    | volleyball   |

